725388f-a.title: Queens: 50th Avenue - 21st Street
725388f-a.text:
50th Avenue, west from 21st Street. Directly
across the street from the garage, where autotmobiles

725384f-a.title: Queens: 50th Avenue - 21st Street
725384f-a.text:
50th Avenue, south side, at 21st Street (vantage point). The
view is southwestward across empty lots, which mark the line of the
new elevated concrete highway, running parallel to the Long Island
Railroad tracks, leading to the hueens-Midtown Tunnel plaza, a few
blocks away. The factory buildings on the left are on 21st Street
